-- Sarkozy Orders Fuel Depots to Be Unblocked, Repeats Reform to Be Completed
-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 2010-10-20T08:28:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/sarkozy-orders-fuel-depots-to-be-unblocked-repeats-reform-to-be-completed.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy
today ordered the removal of blockades at all fuel depots across
the country.  Sarkozy, speaking to ministers at the weekly cabinet
meeting, repeated he will continue with his planned reform of
the French pensions system.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Rhinds at 
 srhinds@bloomberg.net  